{"tid":1511310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"空姐J圖 多圖","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:12:42.000Z","uid":275994,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"70ff7ba056998c6e32ae5a5a235754d37f0d3186","tid":1511310,"uid":275994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:24:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醒啦航空界為左香港而被清算緊 你重想睇J圖</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日國泰，港龍既白色恐佈政治迫害只係開始。除時都可以轉到其他人其他行業。 譚惠珠話:航空業員不應對政治有特別看法。以飛行安全嘅理去禁聲。到時揸巴士，揸的士，揸地鐵甚至飲食業，醫療界都可以話以安全理由要禁聲。<br />\n<br />\n自從國泰新CEO上任就對員工作出清算，所以我哋要從國泰無理解雇員工依件事上比到其他行業，公司，政府甚至中央知道我哋唔會因為咁而屈服。所以828要企出黎圍堵國泰城。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圍到空姐空少返唔到工 飛機唔夠Manpower 自然要cancel飛唔到。</span></span><br />\n唔好再盲撐國泰 轉左CEO已經唔同晒<br />\n今日國泰 當下香港<br />\n搞唔到機場搞國泰一樣咁有影響力<br />\n星期三唔使返工嘅同我黎國泰城<br />\n</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cX4DtvG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcX4DtvG.png&h=a5ebc177&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/im848vH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fim848vH.png&h=cb04af20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f1b47801626de44daa49225f9debebea74198a6","tid":1511310,"uid":198389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/suRKmvs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRKmvs.gif&h=09fb3e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuc